      "evidenceType": "source_excerpt",
      "method": "extraction",
      "sourceRef": "kontourai-flow-agents-413/evidence.json",
      "excerptOrSummary": "Source review of src/cli/workflow-sidecar.ts confirms the iteration-2 Fix-5 hard-refuse tier (non-git repoRoot + sealed commit_sha => refuse) has been fully removed: checkpointHeadAncestry mismatchKind==\"none\" (which includes the non-git-repoRoot case, no resolvable HEAD) is an unconditional allow in publishDelivery, with only mismatchKind==\"positive\" (real cross-repo mismatch) and \"undeterminable-shallow\" (warn-and-allow) retained as the Fix4 tiers. Doc comments at workflow-sidecar.ts:3393-3529 and :4212-4278 explicitly document the iteration-3 revert and its rationale (restores the SUPPORTED non-git-repoRoot scratch/checkpoint-signing flow that iteration-2 regressed).",
      "observedAt": "2026-07-06T06:32:22Z",
      "collectedBy": "flow-agents/workflow-sidecar",
      "passing": true
    },
